Imports CrystalDecisions.Windows.Forms Imports CrystalDecisions.Shared Imports CrystalDecisions.CrystalReports.Engine Imports System Imports System.Windows.Forms
Public Class Snippet
Public Shared Function func(ByVal reportfile As System.String) As System.Array Dim crwreport As CrystalDecisions.CrystalReports.Engine.ReportDocument Try crwreport = New CrystalDecisions.CrystalReports.Engine.ReportDocument Catch ex As Exception Return new String() {"#ERR " + ex.Message} Exit Function End Try Try crwreport.Load(reportfile, OpenReportMethod.OpenReportByTempCopy) Catch ex As Exception Return new string() {"#ERR " + ex.Message} Exit Function End Try dim i,j as Integer dim vs as String dim pv as CrystalDecisions.Shared.ParameterValues Dim pva As CrystalDecisions.Shared.ParameterDiscreteValue 'MessageBox.Show("AnzahlParameter " + crwreport.ParameterFields.Count.ToString) If crwreport.ParameterFields.Count > 0 Then Dim myparams(crwreport.ParameterFields.Count - 1) As String 'dim myarray as Array = Array.CreateInstance(GetType(String), crwreport.ParameterFields.Count) dim myarray(crwreport.ParameterFields.Count-1) as String For i = 0 To crwreport.ParameterFields.Count - 1 If crwreport.ParameterFields(i).Name.StartsWith("Pm-") Then myarray.SetValue(";;;", i) Else 'myparams(i) = crwreport.ParameterFields(i).Name + ";" + crwreport.ParameterFields(i).ParameterValueType.ToString vs = "" pv = crwreport.ParameterFields(i).DefaultValues if pv isnot nothing 'messagebox.show("Defaults "+i.ToString) if pv.Count>0 then for j=0 to pv.Count-1 if vs>"" then vs = vs + "|" pva = pv.Item(j) vs = vs + pva.Value.ToString 'messagebox.show("Wert nach "+j.ToString+" "+vs) next end if end if myarray.SetValue(crwreport.ParameterFields(i).Name + ":" + crwreport.ParameterFields(i).Reportname + ";" + crwreport.ParameterFields(i).ParameterValueType.ToString+";"+vs+";"+crwreport.ParameterFields(i).EnableAllowEditingDefaultValue.ToString,i) End If 'messagebox.show("Parameter "+i.ToString+": "+ myarray(i)) Next Return myarray else Return new String(){"no value"} End If End Function End Class
